data.description: You have the RARE opportunity to own this Executive Estate positioned at the pinnacle of the cul-de-sac on almost .75 acres inside the gated community of The Timbers of Lake Ridge where homes rarely come on the market for sale!!! Inviting foyer & sweeping staircase overlook the open island kitchen with granite counters, decorative backsplash, stainless steel appliances, 5-burner gas cooktop with decorative vent hood, 42 cabinets & 2 pantries!!! Secluded master suite with an attached 12x10 flex room, separate comfort height granite vanities & a walk-in closet with built-in cabinets give you storage galore!!! Downstairs designated office with a wall of built-ins & French doors. 3 bedrooms upstairs & a gameroom with a wet bar overlooks a large balcony. Dual laundry areas (upstairs & downstairs). Breathtaking, park-like views of mature trees & beautiful landscape flank the resort-style pool & spa that are great for entertaining your guest and plenty of room for the kids to run and play!!!
